    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay okay, I hear you. the doctor's clinic is actually closed now so I really do need to do something tonight. if I can't use aspirin, what exactly should I be giving him and how much? i have some infant paracetamol and some adult ibuprofen here, can I just give him a dose of that to get him through the night?",
